A Studio Ghibli style illustration of a serene Singapore cityscape at golden hour, featuring the Marina Bay skyline with its distinctive architecture reflected in calm waters. In the foreground, a person sits peacefully on a wooden dock, surrounded by floating paper origami cranes and neatly organized stacks of colorful folders that drift gently in a warm breeze. The scene conveys a sense of calm productivity and mindful organization, with soft watercolor-like clouds painted in warm oranges and pinks. Lush tropical plants frame the edges of the composition, and small fireflies begin to emerge as evening approaches, adding a magical quality to this moment of focused tranquility.
